name: Get Configuration Drift
description:
Compares a defined configuration in the input XML file with the device current configuration and displays whether it is compliant with it or not.
Lists the non compliant items and the file size, checksum and last write time information of all found files.

inputs.description: Maximum random delay set to avoid network overload. Provide number of seconds lower than 600
inputs.name: MaximumDelayInSeconds

inputs.description: UNC Path where the XML Configuration file is located. Example":" \\\\server\\SharedFolder\\configuration.xml"
inputs.name: ConfigurationFilePath

outputs.description: Whether all categories are compliant or not (Yes/No)
outputs.name: OverallCompliance

outputs.description: Whether all the Windows Registry items in the provided XML configuration file are compliant or not (Yes/No)
outputs.name: RegistryCompliance

outputs.description: Whether all the Windows Services items in the provided XML configuration file are compliant or not (Yes/No)
outputs.name: ServicesCompliance

outputs.description: Whether all the Files and Directories items in the provided XML configuration file are compliant or not (Yes/No)
outputs.name: FilesDirectoriesCompliance

outputs.description: List of Windows Registry paths which were not found
outputs.name: RegistryPathNotFoundItems

outputs.description: List of Windows Registry properties paths whose properties did not match criteria supplied
outputs.name: RegistryPropertyNotFoundItems

outputs.description: List of Windows Registry properties paths whose type did not match criteria supplied
outputs.name: RegistryPropertyTypeNonCompliantItems

outputs.description: List of Windows Registry properties paths whose value did not match criteria supplied
outputs.name: RegistryValueNonCompliantItems

outputs.description: List of Windows Services names which were not found
outputs.name: ServiceNotFoundItems

outputs.description: List of Windows Services names whose startup type did not match criteria supplied
outputs.name: ServiceStartUpTypeNonCompliantItems

outputs.description: List of Windows Services names whose current state did not match criteria supplied
outputs.name: ServiceCurrentStatusNonCompliantItems

outputs.description: List of Files and Directories paths which were not found
outputs.name: FileDirectoryNotFoundItems

outputs.description: List of Files whose SHA256 checksum did not match criteria supplied
outputs.name: FileChecksumNonCompliantItems

outputs.description: List of the File's size of each found file in KB
outputs.name: FileSizeItems

outputs.description: List of the File's SHA256 checksum of each found file
outputs.name: FileChecksumItems

outputs.description: List of the File's last modification date of each found file
outputs.name: FileLastModifiedItems
